'''Orlando Daniel Gill Noldin''' (born 11 June 2000) is a Paraguayan professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for the [[Argentine Primera División]] club [[San Lorenzo de Almagro|San Lorenzo]] and the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]].

==Club career==
Gill is a youth product of the Paraguayan clubs Club 13 de Junio and [[Club Sportivo San Lorenzo|CS San Lorenzo]], and began his senior career with [[Club Sportivo San Lorenzo|CS San Lorenzo]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tycsports.com/san-lorenzo/dura-historia-orlando-gill-vendio-todo-mantener-familia-id685567.html|title=La dura historia de Orlando Gill, el arquero que "vendió todo" para mantener a su familia - TyC Sports|date=12 September 2025|website=www.tycsports.com}}</ref> On 30 December 2023, Gill joined the Argentine club [[San Lorenzo de Almagro]] on loan with an option to buy, and was originally assigned to their reserves.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://onefootball.com/es/noticias/quien-es-orlando-gill-nuevo-arquero-de-san-lorenzo-38800400|title=¿Quién es Orlando Gill, nuevo arquero de San Lorenzo?|date=11 October 2025|website=OneFootball}}</ref> On 21 January 2025, he was bought outright by San Lorenzo de Almagro promoted to their senior team on a contract until 2027.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pagina12.com.ar/798419-ni-keylor-ni-el-holandes-san-lorenzo-apuesta-por-orlando-gil|title=Ni Keylor ni el holandés, San Lorenzo apuesta por Orlando Gill &#124; Compró la mitad del pase del arquero paraguayo|date=21 January 2025|website=PAGINA12}}</ref>

==International career==
Gill was called up to the [[Paraguay national under-20 football team|Paraguay U20]]s for the [[2019 South American U-20 Championship]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.apf.org.py/espanol/los-23-albirrojos-elegidos-para-el-sudamericano-4?nid=3013|title=Los 23 albirrojos elegidos para el Sudamericano &#124; Asociación Paraguaya de Fútbol|website=Asociación Paraguaya de Fútbol}}</ref> He debuted with the senior [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]] for a 1–0 [[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification]] win over [[Peru national football team|Peru national team]] on 6 September 2025.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ole.com.ar/san-lorenzo/san-lorenzo-gill-paraguay_0_joES8MvWPD.html|title=La transformación de Gill: de la apuesta de San Lorenzo al debut soñado en Paraguay|first=Diario Deportivo|last=Olé|date=10 September 2025|website=Olé}}</ref>

